    <p><a name="1"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="1">I:</a> The Fede Imperialis<br><br>~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="1">A</a> Spiritu Dominatus,<br><br>Domine, libra nos</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">From the lightning of the Tempest,<br><br>Our Emperor deliver us<br><br>From plauge, temptation, and war,</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">Our Emperor deliver us.<br><br>From the scourge of the Kraken,<br><br>Our Emperor deliver us.<br><br>From the blasphemies of the falllen,<br><br>Our Emperor deliver us.<br><br>From the begetting of daemons,<br><br>Our Emperor deliver us.<br><br>From the curse of the mutant,<br><br>Our Emperor deliver us.<br><br>A morte perpetua,<br><br>Domine, libra nos<br><br>That thou shouldst spare none,<br><br>That Thou shouldst pardon none,<br><br>That thou wouldst bring them only death.<br><br>We beseech thee, destroy them.<br><br>~<br><br></p>
    <hr>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><br><br><a name="2"></a></h3>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="2">II: The Adoration of the God Emperor</a></h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br>~<br><a name="2">Love</a> the God-Emperor,<br><br>For He is the salvation of mankind.<br><br>Obey His words,<br><br>for He will lead you to the light of the future.<br><br>Heed His wisdom,<br><br>for He will protect you from evil.<br><br>Whisper His prayers in devotion,<br><br>for He will save your soul.<br><br>Honour His Servants,<br><br>for they speak in His voice.<br><br>Tremble before His majesty,<br><br>for we all walk in His immortal shadow.</p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~<br><br></h3>
    <hr>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><a name="3"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="3">III: The Virtue of Service<br></a></h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;">Offer your Heart and Lips to Him<br><br>Offer your body and soul<br><br>To offer up your life and limb<br><br>Is to let Him be with you in whole<br><br><br><br>For only the faithful is mercy bestowed<br><br>Only to those who His word uphold</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="3">Death</a> is a virtue that&apos;s earned and not owed</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">One only granted to those who are bold</p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br></p>
    <hr>
    <p><br></p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br></p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="4"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="4">IV:</a> Prayer of Devotion<br><br><br></h3>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="4">O&apos;</a> God-Emperor who is strength, I devote this life to you.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor who is grace, I devote this life to you.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor who is mercy, I devote this life to you.</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">O&apos; God-Emperor who is valour, I devote this life to you.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor who is light, I devote this life to you.<br><br></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><br></p>
    <hr>
    <p><br></p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><a name="5"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="5" target="_self">V:</a> A Battle Prayer of the Ordos Hereticus<br><br><br><br></h3>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;">O&apos; God-Emperor, be with me as I walk in the darkness.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor, watch over me as I carry Your light.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor, armour me as I battle the wicked.<br><br>O&apos; God-Emperor, surround me and restore me so that I may serve You always,<br><br>In life and in death.</p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><br></p>
    <hr>
    <p><br></p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><a name="6"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="6">VI:</a> Battle Benediction<br><br><br></h3>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="6">Through</a> trials, may the God-Emperor make me resolute.<br><br>Through suffering, may the God-Emperor make me strong.<br><br>Through pain, may the God-Emperor make me worthy.<br><br>Through death, may the God Emperor make me whole.</p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><br></p>
    <hr>
    <p><br></p>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><a name="7"></a></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="7">VII: The</a> Ninth Battle Prayer of the Order of the Sacred Rose<br><br><br></h3>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><a name="7">Be</a> the agent of my blade-arm.</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">Be the power in my armor.<br><br>Be the spirit that guides my bolts into the flesh of foes.<br><br>Be the fire in my heart.<br><br>Be the force that drives my blood.<br><br>God-Emperor of Man, You are all we truly have or need.<br><br>Move me, move through me, all in service to Your divine, perfect will.<br><br>By this may all our enemies be undone and your name be glorified above all.<br><br></p>
    <h3 style="text-align: center;">~</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center;"><br><br><br></p>
